    <item>
      <title>意大利电信签署 15 亿欧元过桥贷款用于再融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/telecom-italia-signs-1-5-billion-bridge-loan-for-refinancing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telecom Italia SpA 已签署 15 亿欧元（16 亿美元）过桥贷款，以满足其完成网络出售之前的再融资需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/telecom-italia-signs-1-5-billion-bridge-loan-for-refinancing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:59:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于电动汽车增长放缓，电池制造商 LG 能源利润暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/profit-at-battery-maker-lg-energy-plunges-amid-slower-ev-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LG Energy Solution Ltd. 的利润大幅下滑，原因是电动汽车增长放缓损害了该电池制造商的出货量和盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/profit-at-battery-maker-lg-energy-plunges-amid-slower-ev-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 06:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《勇者斗恶龙》顶级制作人因 Square Enix 重组而辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/top-dragon-quest-producer-steps-down-in-square-enix-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，史克威尔艾尼克斯控股公司旗舰《勇者斗恶龙》系列的首席制作人将辞去这一职务，因为该系列的下一部作品的开发工作被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/top-dragon-quest-producer-steps-down-in-square-enix-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:45:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新的进口限制后，苹果 MacBook 在印度尼西亚的销量很低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/apple-macbooks-running-low-in-indonesia-after-fresh-import-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚增加国内生产商品的举措已经开始适得其反，公司警告称，包括苹果公司 MacBook Pro 在内的产品供应最快可能在 4 月底开始耗尽。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/apple-macbooks-running-low-in-indonesia-after-fresh-import-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 05:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
